metadata.name: ForestRanger #1
metadata.description:
Forest Ranger is a Collection of 9990 Characters. They are the 3rd collection of JungleParty and will become the central component of our ecosystem with unprecedented utilities. 

Holders of Forest Ranger will be lifetime shareholder of our upcoming casino, they will enjoy lifetime dividend sharing and the highest passive income from staking. The NFT also grants access to custom NFT toolbox.
